						               													<description>A board game for up to 5 players set in a dark future which the first player to collect 6 Spheres of energy wins. Players can choose their hero, get support, fulfill secret objectives, make a deal with other players -or betray them-, explore in search of Spheres, fight and truncate the moves of your rivals.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players can share Deck in Free Play, create two different Decks in Theme Mode, or choose their favorite cards to build a custom Deck in Tournament Mode.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to get Spheres?&amp;#10;- Fulfilling secret Objectives.&amp;#10;- Finding them while Exploring.&amp;#10;- Stealing from other players.&amp;#10;- Defeating 6 enemies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On their turn, each player can:&amp;#10;- Stand up their cards.&amp;#10;- Play a Character from their hand.&amp;#10;- Explore or Attack with each Character.&amp;#10;- Draw cards until have 6.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Anytime:&amp;#10;- Play Action cards.&amp;#10;- Play an accomplished Objective card.&amp;#10;- Activate effects of any Character.&amp;#10;- Propose a Pact to another player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first player to collect 6 Spheres is the winner. There are different ways to get them, so keep an eye on the other players and guess their intentions!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
